    {
      "id": "n2",
      "label": "Bespoke shed company",
      "nested": null,
      "resources": [
        {
          "id": "meta-1",
          "title": "TheBrain metadata",
          "url": "",
          "note": "kind=1 | created=2025-12-30T11:25:56.6709969 | modified=2025-12-30T11:26:18.9278979",
          "addedAt": "2026-04-22T22:19:00+01:00"
        },
        {
          "id": "note-1",
          "title": "Notes",
          "url": "",
          "note": "**Create a clear, presentation-ready mind map with balanced depth and readable labels.**\n** Use descriptive node names, logical grouping, and minimal repetition.**\n---\n### **Central Node**\n**Bespoke Sheds \u2014 Automated Physical Infrastructure**\n---\n### **Vision & North Star**\n* Core purpose: turning human intent into made-to-order buildings\n* Technical North Star: intent \u2192 automated physical infrastructure\n* Plain-language North Star:\n\t* \u201cYou explain what you want to use a space for, and a custom building is designed and built for you\u201d\n* Long-term system, not a single product\n---\n### **Core Principles**\n* Intent-first design (use before specifications)\n* Single source of truth (parametric 3D model)\n* Visual cognition over text-heavy interfaces\n* Manufacturing realism and constraint awareness\n* No-drift, deterministic engineering discipline\n---\n### **System Architecture**\n* **Customer Interface**\n\t* Visual, web-based configurator\n\t* Intent-driven inputs\n* **Design Intelligence**\n\t* Parametric rules\n\t* Structural feasibility\n\t* Cost feedback\n* **Commitment & Ordering**\n\t* Pricing lock\n\t* Versioned design snapshot\n* **Manufacturing Translation**\n\t* Bills of materials\n\t* Cutting lists\n\t* CNC-ready outputs\n* **Delivery & Installation**\n\t* Logistics planning\n\t* Assembly sequencing\n* **Future Automation**\n\t* CNC optimisation\n\t* Robotics\n\t* Modular systems\n---\n### **Technical Foundation (Current State)**\n* Working parametric 3D engine\n* Wall, roof, base, insulation logic\n* Manufacturing-aware BOM generation\n* Accurate cutting lists with real constraints\n* Stable, inspectable codebase\n---\n### **Roadmap (Living & Capability-Based)**\n* Foundations (largely complete)\n* Intent \u2192 Design simplification\n* Design \u2192 Commitment (commercial viability)\n* Production optimisation\n* Physical automation (long horizon)\n---\n### **Vertical Use-Cases**\n* Garden offices and workshops\n* Wellness spaces\n* Production sheds\n\t* Food\n\t* Drink\n\t* Controlled environments\n* Future micro-infrastructure modules\n---\n### **Narrative & Communication**\n* Customer messaging: explain use, not specs\n* Partner messaging: efficiency and automation\n* Investor messaging: scalable system architecture\n* Public language rules\n\t* Avoid jargon\n\t* Avoid AI hype\n\t* Anchor explanations in real-world use\n---\n### **Funding & Partnerships**\n* Materials and tooling sponsorship\n* Manufacturing and fabrication partners\n* Strategic angel investors\n* Grants and innovation funding\n* Content-led sponsorship opportunities\n---\n### **Operating Model**\n* Project Memory Schema for continuity\n* Layer-based system thinking\n* Visual-first planning and explanation\n* Strict scope and change discipline\n* Long-term system execution mindset",
          "addedAt": "2026-04-22T22:19:00+01:00"
        }
      ]
    },
